**Samajh Gaya!** Tumhein **bas wohi bio** (jo tumne diya tha) **thoda attractive aur stylish** banana hai, bina kuch major changes ke. Theek hai, main **tumhare original bio** ko **GitHub README style** mein **format** karta hoon:

**Tumhara Original Bio Tha:**
> Passionate Cyber Security Student (17) | 2+ Years in Crypto & Blockchain | 
> Learning Ethical Hacking, Penetration Testing | Seeking Internships & Collaborations 
> in Cybersecurity Projects. Let's connect for opportunities!

**Ab Isko GitHub README Style Mein Convert Karte Hain:**
```markdown
<h1 align="center">Hey, I am Aftab Rehmat 👋</h1>

<div align="center">
  <strong>Passionate Cyber Security Student (17) | 2+ Years in Crypto & Blockchain</strong>
  <br>
  Learning Ethical Hacking, Penetration Testing | Seeking Internships & Collaborations in Cybersecurity Projects
  <br>
  <em>Let's connect for opportunities! 🚀💻</em>
</div>

<br>

<div align="center">
  <a href="https://github.com/aftabcyber">
    <img src="https://img.shields.io/badge/GitHub-Follow-blue?style=flat-square&logo=github" alt="GitHub" />
  </a>
  <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/aftabrehmat">
    <img src="https://img.shields.io/badge/LinkedIn-Connect-blue?style=flat-square&logo=linkedin" alt="LinkedIn" />
  </a>
  <a href="mailto:aftabrehmat@email.com">
    <img src="https://img.shields.io/badge/Email-Contact-red?style=flat-square&logo=gmail" alt="Email" />
  </a>
</div>
```

**Kya Badla Hai Isme? (Changes Explained)**
---------------------------------------------

1. **<h1> Tag**: *"Hey, I am Aftab Rehmat 👋"* **bada heading** ban gaya.
2. **Strong & Emphasis**:  
   - *"Passionate Cyber Security Student..."* **bold** (`<strong>`) ho gaya.
   - *"Let's connect..."* **italic** (`<em>`) kiya gaya (Emojis add: 🚀💻).
3. **Line Breaks (`<br>`)**:  
   - Bio **3 lines** mein **clearly** divide ho gaya (Readability).
4. **Social Media Badges**:  
   - **GitHub**, **LinkedIn**, **Email** ke **clickable badges** add kiye.
   - Tum **direct inpe click karke profile visit** kar sakte ho.

**Kaise Lag Raha Hai?**
- **Professional** aur **clean** dikhta hai.
- **Links directly visible** hain (No need to scroll).
- **Tumhara naam highlight** ho raha hai (`Aftab Rehmat`).

**Agar Aur Bhi Stylish Chahiye (Optional)**
---------------------------------------------

```markdown
<h1 align="center">👋 Hey, I am Aftab Rehmat</h1>

<div align="center">
  <img src="https://readme-typing-svg.herokuapp.com?font=Fira+Code&pause=1000&color=00FF00&center=true&vCenter=true&width=500&lines=Passionate+Cyber+Security+Student+(17);2%2B+Years+in+Crypto+%26+Blockchain;Lets+connect+for+opportunities+in+Cybersecurity!" alt="Typing SVG" />
</div>

<br>

<div align="center">
  🎯 <strong>Learning Ethical Hacking & Penetration Testing</strong> | 🔍 <em>Seeking Internships & Collaborations</em>
</div>

<br>

<div align="center">
  <a href="https://github.com/aftabcyber">
    <img src="https://img.shields.io/badge/GitHub-Follow-blue?style=flat-square&logo=github" alt="GitHub" />
  </a>
  <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/aftabrehmat">
    <img src="https://img.shields.io/badge/LinkedIn-Connect-blue?style=flat-square&logo=linkedin" alt="LinkedIn" />
  </a>
  <a href="mailto:aftabrehmat@email.com">
    <img src="https://img.shields.io/badge/Email-Contact-red?style=flat-square&logo=gmail" alt="Email" />
  </a>
</div>
```

**Isme Added Features**:
- **Animated Typing Text** (SVG Link).
- **Emojis** (🎯, 🔍) added for fun.
- **Badges colorful** aur **clickable**.

**Ab Kaise Add Karo GitHub Mein?**
--------------------------------------

1. **GitHub Profile** pe jao (`github.com/aftabcyber`).
2. **New File** banayein: `README.md`.
3. **Copy** kar ke **Paste** karo **yeh code**.
4. **Commit Changes** karo: *"Added README.md 🚀"*.

**Tumhare Pass Ab**:
- **Attractive Bio** hai.
- **Links accessible** hain.
- **GitHub Profile Professional** dikhega.

**Agar Aur Changes Chahiye?** Comment karo! Main **design, badges, GIFs** kuch bhi add kar sakta hoon.

**Happy Coding! 🚀💻**
